@msisj For the tests to verify parameter types and formatting,  I would add a file tests/unit/test_container_create.py and tests/unit/test_pod_create.py that way you can just mock up the server code.

If you want to verify the service API results then tests/integration/test_container_create.py and tests/integration/test_pod_create.py would be my suggestions.

Does that make sense? Help? Thanks for all your work on this PR!
